{"date":"1928-11-18","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/38/2e/113650_guw55.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/38/2e/113650_guw55.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/38/2e/113650_guw55.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/38/2e/113650_guw55.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/38/2e/113650_guw55.jpg"},"summary":"《汽船威利号》（Steamboat Willie）是华特迪士尼全球第一出有声的动画片，动画片的主角是著名的米奇老鼠。此影片于1928年11月18日在纽约79街殖民大戏院（Colony Theater）上映，米老鼠的生日便定为了那天。\r\n\r\n片内的米老鼠没有说话，只随着轻快的音乐跃动和吹口哨。其形象博得观众的喜欢，并轰动了全纽约。随即米老鼠就成了举世闻名的“明星”。1932年，这部影片更获得了奥斯卡的特别奖。 据说上映时，纽约人到场看的并非剧情，而是这只可爱的老鼠，在这八分钟内彻底的娱乐了在座的市民们。\r\n","name":"Steamboat Willie","name_cn":"汽船威利号","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":75},{"name":"Disney","count":55},{"name":"1928","count":45},{"name":"欧美","count":43},{"name":"迪士尼","count":35},{"name":"美国","count":20},{"name":"米老鼠","count":19},{"name":"万恶之源","count":15},{"name":"考古","count":15},{"name":"奥斯卡","count":15},{"name":"原创","count":14},{"name":"先驱","count":9},{"name":"始祖","count":7},{"name":"剧场版","count":6},{"name":"1920-1929","count":3},{"name":"1928年11月","count":2},{"name":"搞笑","count":2},{"name":"短篇","count":2},{"name":"UbIwerks","count":2},{"name":"1928年","count":1},{"name":"Short_film","count":1},{"name":"1900-1949","count":1},{"name":"世界上第一部有声动画","count":1},{"name":"剧场版-01","count":1},{"name":"20年代","count":1},{"name":"【ANIME】短片丨美国","count":1},{"name":"系列短片","count":1},{"name":"undefined","count":1},{"name":"Walt.Disney.Pictures","count":1},{"name":"欢乐","count":1}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"汽船威利号"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1928年11月18日"},{"key":"片长","value":"8分钟"},{"key":"导演","value":"Walt Disney / Ub Iwerks"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":1342,"total":164,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":2,"5":5,"6":19,"7":70,"8":47,"9":11,"10":10},"score":7.4},"total_episodes":1,"collection":{"on_hold":6,"dropped":6,"wish":29,"collect":263,"doing":4},"id":113650,"eps":1,"volumes":0,"locked":false,"ns